This file describes the steps that are required to migrate an
existing eZ Lightbox installation from a minor release of the
0.7 series to a minor release of the 0.8 series.

0.7.x to 0.8.0
==============

Javascript function "changeCurrentLightbox()"
---------------------------------------------

If the javascript function "changeCurrentLightbox()" is used
in any other than the default templates, this function must be
renamed to "eZLightboxLibrary.changeCurrentLightbox()"

